Už nepríde.

124
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,959
To, čo si videla,

125
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,339
sú len jej spomienky.

126
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,240
Všetko sú to ilúzie.

127
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,060
Všetko.

128
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:30,660
Čo ste to videli?

129
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,180
Videli sme pravdu.

130
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:38,579
Ale pravdu...

131
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,420
